                <h1 class="account-header account-header-low-margin-top">Complex Symfony2 Examples: Users, Menus, CMS Features</h1>
                
                                    <p class="hidden-xs">
                        Course:
                        <a class="knp-color-black" href="../question-answer-day.1"><em>Question and Answer Day: March 27th, 2013 Tutorial</em></a>                    </p>
